  "texts": [
    "The work proposed using hackathons as a practical learning approach in cybersecurity education.",
    "The study explores the integration of a series of online hackathon events into an online cybersecurity course.",
    "The objective is to address issues associated with online education by fostering collaboration and enhancing students' practical understanding through solving real-world challenges.",
    "The findings suggest that the interventions introduced, which support teamwork and collaboration, maintain student participation and interest, and promote learning-by-doing, are attributed to learning benefits by students.",
    "The work in Srivatanakul and Annansingh (2022) focused on designing and developing a degree course in software and web security at York College of the City University of New York (CUNY), using active learning strategies."
  ],
